                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7112" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0220</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9092 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钻石梦碎：豫金刚石深陷掏空泥潭</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shattered Dreams: Yu Diamond Suffers from Hollowing Out</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李秀珠，施棋，张玉滢，肖厚奎，梁蓥，黄健萱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州华晶金刚石股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大股东掏空；关联方交易；违规担保</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shareholders hollowed out;Related Party Transactions;Illegal guarantees</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，大股东掏空成为上市公司业绩变脸的重要原因之一，大股东掏空不仅对企业价值和广大投资者的利益造成严重损害，也在一定程度上破坏了创业板市场的制度环境。2020年，豫金刚石业绩变脸事件引发了广泛的关注，而大股东掏空是导致豫金刚石业绩巨变的根源。本案例以豫金刚石为研究对象，以其业绩变脸事件为切入点，探究豫金刚石业绩“暴雷”的真相。通过详细描述豫金刚石与其他方反常的商业行为揭示豫金刚石隐蔽的关联方关系以及大股东对豫金刚石的一系列掏空行为，希望帮助学员理解、分析豫金刚石大股东为什么想要掏空公司、为什么能够掏空公司以及大股东掏空豫金刚石的手段，并引导学员思考如何对大股东掏空上市公司的行为进行防范。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years,the hollowing out of major shareholders has become one of the important reasons for the change in the performance of listed companies.The hollowing out of major shareholders has not only caused serious damage to the corporate value and the interests of the majority of investors,but also destroyed the institutional environment of the Growth Enterprise Market to a certain extent.In 2020,the changing face of Yu Diamond&#39;s performance has attracted widespread attention,and the hollowing out of major shareholders is the root cause of the great change in Yu Diamond&#39;s performance.This case takes Yu Diamond as the research object,and takes its performance-changing event as the starting point,leads to the exploration of the truth of Yu Diamond&#39;s performance &quot;tornado&quot;,and reveals the hidden related parties of Yu Diamond by describing in detail the abnormal business behavior of Yu Diamond and other parties.We hope to help students understand and analyze why the major shareholders of Yu Diamond want to hollow out the company,why they can hollow out the company and the methods of the major shareholders to hollow out Yu Diamond,and guide students to think how to prevent the behavior of major shareholders hollowing out listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称理论；内部控制理论委托代理理论、控制权和现金流量权偏离；掏空方式；关联方及关联交易；从内部控制和公司治理角度防范大股东掏空行为</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
